                     <interp inst="t18501125-41-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>, stealing 1 tame rabbit, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the property of <persName id="t18501125-name-180" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18501125-name-180" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
